' @test valid
' @covers RESULT, LIST, TEXT, CHOICE
' @description RESULT with nested LIST containing multiple typed fields

THINK plan
  GOAL <<
  Create an implementation plan.
  >>
  RESULT
  * summary: TEXT - plan overview
  * steps: LIST - implementation steps
    * description: TEXT - what to do
    * effort: CHOICE(small, medium, large) - estimated effort
    * dependencies: TEXT - what this step depends on
END

WAIT
  ON ?plan
END

EXIT
